<xsl:stylesheet version="2.0" 
xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform"
xmlns:map="http://www.w3.org/2005/xpath-functions/map"
xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
    <xsl:template match="/">
        <output>
            
            <!-- Loop over Table array -->
            <xsl:for-each
                select="/ObjectNode/queryResult">
            <xsl:variable name="customerOrder_extid" select="/ObjectNode/result/content/data/head/fields/verw/value" />
            <xsl:variable name="cd_product_extid" select="concat(./productionorder_extid, '_' , ./cd_product_extid)" />
            <xsl:variable name="productionorder_extid" select="./productionorder_extid" />
            <xsl:variable name="cd_department_extid" select="./cd_department_extid" />
            <xsl:variable name="cd_machinetype_extid_db" select="./cd_machinetype_extid" />
            <xsl:variable name="cd_machine_extid" select="./cd_machine_extid" />
            <xsl:variable name="cd_productionstep_extid" select="./cd_productionstep_extid" />
            <xsl:variable name="cD_ToolType_extid" select="concat(/ObjectNode/result/content/data/head/fields/banummer/text, '_', ./fields/elemnum/value)" />
            <xsl:variable name="machineoccupation_extid" select="./machineoccupation_extid" />
            <xsl:variable name="cD_Tool_extid" select="concat(/ObjectNode/result/content/data/head/fields/banummer/text, '_', ./fields/elemnum/value)" />
            <xsl:variable name="cD_ProductRelationship_extid" select="concat(/ObjectNode/result/content/data/head/fields/banummer/text, '_REL_', /ObjectNode/result/content/data/head/fields/artnum/value, '_', ./fields/elemnum/value)" />
            <xsl:variable name="cd_machinetype_extid">
                <xsl:choose>
                    <xsl:when test="$cd_machinetype_extid_db = 10 or $cd_machinetype_extid_db = 11">
                        <xsl:value-of select="'001'"/>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when test="$cd_machinetype_extid_db = 12">
                        <xsl:value-of select="'002'"/>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when test="$cd_machinetype_extid_db = 9">
                        <xsl:value-of select="'003'"/>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when test="$cd_machinetype_extid_db = 14">
                        <xsl:value-of select="'004'"/>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when test="$cd_machinetype_extid_db = 15">
                        <xsl:value-of select="'005'"/>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when test="$cd_machinetype_extid_db = 20">
                        <xsl:value-of select="'006'"/>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when test="$cd_machinetype_extid_db = 18">
                        <xsl:value-of select="'007'"/>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when test="$cd_machinetype_extid_db = 19">
                        <xsl:value-of select="'008'"/>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:otherwise>
                        <xsl:value-of select="$cd_machinetype_extid_db"/>
                    </xsl:otherwise>
                </xsl:choose>
            </xsl:variable>
            
            <!-- Customer Order -->
            <customerOrder>
                <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="$customerOrder_extid" />
                </externalId>
                <customerName>
                    <xsl:value-of select="/ObjectNode/result/content/data/head/fields/ykunde/value" />
                </customerName>
                <deadline>
                    <xsl:value-of select="concat(/ObjectNode/result/content/data/head/fields/tterm/value, 'T23:59:00')" />
                </deadline>
                <name>
                    <xsl:value-of select="/ObjectNode/result/content/data/head/fields/verw/value" />
                </name>
            </customerOrder>

            <!-- Product -->
            <cD_Product>
                <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="$cd_product_extid" />
                </externalId>
                
                <name>
                    <xsl:value-of select="parse-json(./cd_product_name/value)?de_DE"/>
                </name>
            </cD_Product>

            <!-- Production Order -->
            <productionOrder>
                <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="$productionorder_extid" />
                </externalId>
                <name>
                    <xsl:value-of select="./productionorder_name" />
                </name>
                <versionNr>
                    <xsl:value-of select="/ObjectNode/additional/versionNr" />
                </versionNr>
                <measurement>
                    <amount>
                        <xsl:value-of select="number(./productionorder_amount)" />
                    </amount>
                    <unitString>pcs</unitString>
                </measurement>
                <deadline>
                    <xsl:call-template name="timeConversion">
                        <xsl:with-param name="epochTime"><xsl:value-of select="./productionorder_deadline" /></xsl:with-param>
                    </xsl:call-template>
                </deadline>

                <!-- References -->
                <customerOrder>
                    <externalId>
                        <xsl:value-of select="$customerOrder_extid" />
                    </externalId>
                </customerOrder>
                <product>
                    <externalId>
                        <xsl:value-of select="$cd_product_extid" />
                    </externalId>
                </product>
            </productionOrder>
            
            <cD_Department>
                <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="$cd_department_extid" />
                </externalId>
                <name>
                    <xsl:value-of select="./cd_department_name" />
                </name>
            </cD_Department>

            <xsl:choose>
                <xsl:when
                    test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Spritzgießen A' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Spritzgießen B'">
                    <!-- MachineType -->
                    <cD_MachineType>
                        <externalId>
                            <xsl:value-of select="$cd_machinetype_extid" />
                        </externalId>
                        <name>Spritzgießen</name>                        
                        <departments>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$cd_department_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                        </departments>
                    </cD_MachineType>
                   
                </xsl:when>
                <xsl:otherwise>
                    <!-- MachineType -->
                    <cD_MachineType>
                        <externalId>
                            <xsl:value-of select="$cd_machinetype_extid" />
                        </externalId>
                        <name>
                            <xsl:value-of select="./cd_machinetype_name" />
                        </name>                        
                        <departments>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$cd_department_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                        </departments>
                    </cD_MachineType>
                
                </xsl:otherwise>
            </xsl:choose>

                    <!-- Machine -->
                    <cD_Machine>
                        <externalId>
                            <xsl:value-of select="$cd_machine_extid" />
                        </externalId>
                        <name>
                            <xsl:value-of select="./cd_machine_name" />
                        </name>
                        <machineType>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$cd_machinetype_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                        </machineType>
                    </cD_Machine>

            <!-- ProductionStep -->
            <cD_ProductionStep>
                <name>
                    <xsl:value-of select="./cd_productionstep_name" />
                </name>
                <productionDuration>
                    <xsl:value-of select="number(./cd_productionstep_duration)*60 div number(./productionorder_amount)" />
                </productionDuration>
                <setupTime>
                    <xsl:value-of select="number(0)" />
                </setupTime>
                <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="$cd_productionstep_extid" />
                </externalId>
                <machineType>
                    <externalId>
                        <xsl:value-of select="$cd_machinetype_extid" />
                    </externalId>
                </machineType>
                <sequence>
                    <xsl:value-of select="./cd_productionstep_number" />
                </sequence>

                <!-- Check for ArbGang ID and select first id of camunda process -->
                <xsl:choose>
                    <xsl:when
                        test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Spritzgießen A' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Spritzgießen B' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Wickeln' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Tiefziehen'">
                        <camundaProcessName>Subprocess_Basis</camundaProcessName>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when 
                        test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Handmontage' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Endmontage'">
                        <camundaProcessName>Subprocess_Montage</camundaProcessName>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when 
                        test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'QS Prüfung'">
                        <camundaProcessName>Subprocess_QS</camundaProcessName>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when 
                        test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Verpackung'">
                        <camundaProcessName>Subprocess_Verpackung</camundaProcessName>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:when 
                        test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Versand'">
                        <camundaProcessName>Subprocess_Versand</camundaProcessName>
                    </xsl:when>
                    <xsl:otherwise>
                        <camundaProcessName>Subprocess_Basis</camundaProcessName>
                    </xsl:otherwise>
                </xsl:choose>
                
                <product>
                    <externalId>
                        <xsl:value-of select="$cd_product_extid" />
                    </externalId>
                </product>
            </cD_ProductionStep>
                <!--
                    <machineOccupation>
                        <externalId>
                            <xsl:value-of select="$machineoccupation_extid" />
                        </externalId>
                        <name>
                            <xsl:value-of select="./cd_productionstep_number" />
                        </name>
                        <plannedStartDateTime>                            
                            <xsl:call-template name="timeConversion">
                                <xsl:with-param name="epochTime"><xsl:value-of select="./machineoccupation_plannedstart" /></xsl:with-param>
                            </xsl:call-template>
                        </plannedStartDateTime>
                        <plannedEndDateTime>
                            <xsl:call-template name="timeConversion">
                                <xsl:with-param name="epochTime"><xsl:value-of select="./machineoccupation_plannedstart" /></xsl:with-param>
                            </xsl:call-template>
                        </plannedEndDateTime>
                        <productionOrder>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$productionorder_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                        </productionOrder>
                        <department>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$cd_department_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                        </department>
                        <status>READY_TO_START</status>

                        <productionSteps>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$cd_productionstep_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                        </productionSteps>

                        <xsl:choose>
                            <xsl:when
                                test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Spritzgießen A' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Spritzgießen B' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Wickeln' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Tiefziehen'">
                                <camundaProcessName>Process_Basis</camundaProcessName>
                            </xsl:when>
                            <xsl:when 
                                test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Handmontage' or ./cd_machinetype_name = 'Endmontage'">
                                <camundaProcessName>Process_Montage</camundaProcessName>
                            </xsl:when>
                            <xsl:when 
                                test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'QS Prüfung'">
                                <camundaProcessName>Process_Check</camundaProcessName>
                            </xsl:when>
                            <xsl:when 
                                test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Verpackung'">
                                <camundaProcessName>Process_Verpackung</camundaProcessName>
                            </xsl:when>
                            <xsl:when 
                                test="./cd_machinetype_name = 'Versand'">
                                <camundaProcessName>Process_Versand</camundaProcessName>
                            </xsl:when>
                            <xsl:otherwise>
                                <camundaProcessName>Process_Basis</camundaProcessName>
                            </xsl:otherwise>
                        </xsl:choose>
                        <machine>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$cd_machine_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                        </machine>

                    </machineOccupation>-->

                <!-- Produkt/Material -->
                <xsl:if
                    test="./fields/elart/value = '(Product)'">
                    <cD_Product>
                        <name>
                            <xsl:value-of select="json-to-xml(data)/map:map/map:string[@name='de_DE']"/>
                        </name>
                        <externalId>
                            <xsl:value-of select="$cd_product_extid" />
                        </externalId>
                    </cD_Product>
                    <cD_ProductRelationship>
                        <externalId>
                            <xsl:value-of select="$cD_ProductRelationship_extid" />
                        </externalId>
                        <product>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$cd_product_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                            <unitString>pcs</unitString>
                        </product>
                        <part>
                            <externalId>
                                <xsl:value-of select="$cd_product_extid" />
                            </externalId>
                            <unitString>pcs</unitString>
                        </part>
                        <extIdProductionOrder>

                            <xsl:value-of select="$productionorder_extid" />
                        </extIdProductionOrder>
                        <xsl:call-template name="measurement">
                            <xsl:with-param name="amount"><xsl:value-of select="number(./fields/anzahl/value)" /></xsl:with-param>
                            <xsl:with-param name="unitString"><xsl:value-of select="./fields/elemle/value" /></xsl:with-param>
                        </xsl:call-template>
                    </cD_ProductRelationship>
                </xsl:if>
            </xsl:for-each>
        </output>

    </xsl:template>

    <!-- Templates -->
    <xsl:template name="toolSetting">
        <xsl:param name="externalId" />
        <xsl:param name="parameterId" />
        <xsl:param name="value" />
        <toolSetting>
            <externalId><xsl:value-of select="$externalId" />_<xsl:value-of select="$parameterId" /></externalId>
            <settingsValue>
                <xsl:value-of select="$value" />
            </settingsValue>
            <toolSettingParameter>
                <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="$parameterId" />
                </externalId>
            </toolSettingParameter>
            <measurement>
                <amount>0</amount>
                <unitString></unitString>
            </measurement>
        </toolSetting>
    </xsl:template>

    <xsl:template name="measurement">
        <xsl:param name="unitString" />
        <xsl:param name="amount" />
        <measurement>
            <amount>
                <xsl:value-of select="number($amount)" />
            </amount>
            <xsl:if
                test="$unitString = '(G)'">
                <unitString>g</unitString>
            </xsl:if>
            <xsl:if
                test="$unitString = '(PCE)'">
                <unitString>pcs</unitString>
            </xsl:if>
        </measurement>
    </xsl:template>    
    <xsl:template name="timeConversion">
        <xsl:param name="epochTime" />
        <xsl:variable name="milliseconds" select="number(./productionorder_deadline)"/>
        <xsl:variable name="seconds" select="floor($milliseconds div 1000)"/>
        <xsl:variable name="days" select="floor($seconds div 86400)"/>
        <xsl:variable name="remainingSeconds" select="$seconds mod 86400"/>
        <!-- Handle days and remaining seconds separately to avoid large duration issues -->
        <xsl:variable name="epochDate" select="xs:dateTime('1970-01-01T00:00:00')"/>
        <xsl:variable name="dateTimeDays" select="$epochDate + xs:dayTimeDuration(concat('P', $days, 'D'))"/>
        <xsl:variable name="dateTime" select="$dateTimeDays + xs:dayTimeDuration(concat('PT', $remainingSeconds, 'S'))"/>

        <xsl:value-of select="format-dateTime($dateTime, '[Y0001]-[M01]-[D01]T[H01]:[m01]:[s01]')"/>
    </xsl:template>
</xsl:stylesheet>

SELECT
	prod.id as cd_Product_extId,
    prod.name as cd_Product_name,
  
    pr.name as productionOrder_extId,
    pr.name as productionOrder_name,
    pr.date_finished as productionOrder_deadline,
    pr.product_qty as productionOrder_amount,
    
    comp.id as cD_Department_extId,
    comp.name as cD_Department_name,
  
    wc.id as cD_MachineType_extId,
    wc.name as cD_MachineType_name,
  
    wc.id as cD_Machine_extId,
    wc.name as cD_Machine_name,
  
    wo.barcode as cD_ProductionStep_extId,
    wo.name as cD_ProductionStep_name,
    wo.duration_expected as cD_ProductionStep_duration,  
	rwc.sequence as cd_productionstep_number,
	
    wo.barcode as machineOccupation_extId,
    wo.name as machineOccupation_name,
    wo.production_date as machineOccupation_plannedStart
    
	
FROM public.mrp_production pr
JOIN public.res_company comp ON comp.id = pr.company_id
JOIN public.mrp_bom bo ON bo.id = pr.bom_id
JOIN public.product_template prod ON prod.id = bo.product_tmpl_id
JOIN public.mrp_workorder wo ON pr.id = wo.production_id
JOIN public.mrp_workcenter wc ON wc.id = wo.workcenter_id
JOIN public.mrp_routing_workcenter rwc ON rwc.bom_id = pr.bom_id and rwc.workcenter_id = wc.id and rwc.name = wo.name
	
where comp.id = 2 and pr.state = 'confirmed' order by pr.name, rwc.sequence;
